      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God gave us Christ as the rock of our refuge, our rampart,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Cov’ring from tempests, our strength, our protection, our bulwark!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As we entreat, He is our shield and retreat;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Morning by morning, our safeguard!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God stands on Christ, the cleft rock, His own life to deliver!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He comes as Spirit, refreshing us as the Life-giver!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our El Shaddai, our all-sufficient supply,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Flows into us as a river!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Christ is unlimited, flowing, our rock of salvation!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Having done all, He’s awaiting our cooperation!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Simply believe! Speak to the rock and receive!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Drink Him with great jubilation!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our smitten rock has been following us without ceasing,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Ready to flow out, the torrents of God’s life releasing!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Life as a tide streams from the Lord’s wounded side,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thirst quenching, dryness appeasing!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Life springs from death by the power of Christ’s resurrection!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Baptism into His death brings release and protection!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Subjectively, His cross continually"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Deepens the river’s extension!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Dig out the well in the light of the Lord’s inner shining!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Sense the anointing, to His inner feeling aligning;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Prayer after prayer, through the Lord’s leading and care,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our inward parts He’s refining!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The throne of God is the source of this crystalline river,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Heading us up and renewing us for His good pleasure!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His kingdom come! On earth, His will must be done!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His be the glory forever!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Sing songs of praise to the well, to the Christ we embody!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Drink the one Spirit, as members of Christ’s unique Body!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thus sanctified, we are prepared as His Bride,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Purified, spotless, and godly!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Out of our innermost being flows rivers of water!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thus we’re conformed to the Son! What a joy to the Father!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Jerusalem, God fully mingled with man,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Flows forth this river forever!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
